# This directory holds calibration data files.
# turret_calibration_data.csv will be created here when running calibration on the robot.
# To use calibration data:
# 1. Run calibration on robot in test mode
# 2. Download CSV from roboRIO: scp lvuser@roborio-2852-frc.local:/home/lvuser/deploy/calibration/turret_calibration_data.csv src/main/deploy/calibration/
# 3. Build the project: ./gradlew build
# 4. The build will auto-generate TurretLookupTables.java with optimized constants
